# hero-reel: the README hero. A dense SKY130 standard cell rendered in full color, a zoom
# into its transistors, then the 3D layer stack orbits. Every frame is filled colored
# geometry -- never the sparse big-die overview scatter. The media gate (color_buckets_center)
# rejects the capture if any frame goes flat or blank.
viewport 1600x1000
use-case inspect-cell
settle
capture 20 20
zoom 2.0
wait 4
capture 26 20
view3d on
wait 8
orbit 4 0
capture 96 20
